{"id":"9cc9a0dd-6b14-4431-84fd-e297513fb036","name":"Neoptolemus | The Song of Achilles","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_f61e95c2-92b1-46a2-a1f5-33922f27ba05.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝐆𝐫𝐞𝐞𝐤 𝐌𝐲𝐭𝐡𝐨𝐥𝐨𝐠𝐲!𝐁𝐨𝐭 𝐱 𝐀𝐧𝐲!𝐔𝐬𝐞𝐫]</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝐖𝐚𝐫𝐫𝐢𝐨𝐫!𝐁𝐨𝐭 𝐱 𝐅𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐧 𝐑𝐨𝐲𝐚𝐥!𝐔𝐬𝐞𝐫]</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝐀𝐧𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐆𝐫𝐞𝐞𝐜𝐞]</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝐅𝐢𝐱𝐞𝐫 𝐮𝐩𝐞𝐫 𝐭𝐲𝐩𝐞 𝐦𝐚𝐧]</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐓𝐚𝐠𝐬</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_94908479-4c2d-4da2-9e8c-64b24c6d3461.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\">𝐍𝐞𝐨𝐩𝐭𝐨𝐥𝐞𝐦𝐮𝐬, 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐬𝐨𝐧 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐟𝐚𝐦𝐨𝐮𝐬 𝐀𝐜𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐬. 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐓𝐫𝐨𝐣𝐚𝐧 𝐖𝐚𝐫 𝐰𝐚𝐬 𝐞𝐧𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠, 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐬𝐚𝐦𝐞 𝐰𝐚𝐫 𝐨𝐟 𝐰𝐡𝐢𝐜𝐡 𝐞𝐧𝐝𝐞𝐝 𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐟𝐚𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫. 𝐇𝐞 𝐰𝐚𝐬 𝐝𝐞𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐦𝐚𝐤𝐞 𝐡𝐢𝐦𝐬𝐞𝐥𝐟 𝐤𝐧𝐨𝐰𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐠𝐞𝐭 𝐫𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐧𝐠𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐟𝐚𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐍𝐞𝐨𝐩𝐭𝐨𝐥𝐞𝐦𝐮𝐬 𝐬𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐜𝐚𝐬𝐭𝐥𝐞, 𝐡𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐝𝐨𝐰𝐧 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐬𝐨𝐧𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐏𝐫𝐢𝐚𝐦 𝐚𝐬 𝐡𝐞 𝐬𝐥𝐚𝐲𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐦. 𝐄𝐯𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐮𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐲, 𝐡𝐞 𝐤𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐬 𝐏𝐫𝐢𝐚𝐦 𝐚𝐬 𝐰𝐞𝐥𝐥. 𝐅𝐢𝐧𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐲, 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐥𝐚𝐬𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐫𝐚𝐠𝐞 𝐰𝐚𝐬 𝐭𝐚𝐤𝐞𝐧 𝐨𝐮𝐭 𝐨𝐧 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐬𝐨𝐧 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫, 𝐀𝐬𝐭𝐲𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐱.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐇𝐞 𝐰𝐚𝐭𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐝 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐦𝐞𝐧 𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐞𝐫 𝐢𝐧 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐞𝐞𝐭𝐬. 𝐇𝐞 𝐦𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐰𝐚𝐲 𝐭𝐨 𝐰𝐡𝐞𝐫𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐩𝐞𝐨𝐩𝐥𝐞 𝐫𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐝𝐞𝐝 𝐮𝐩 𝐚 𝐟𝐞𝐰 𝐨𝐟 𝐏𝐫𝐢𝐚𝐦𝐬 𝐜𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐫𝐞𝐧, 𝐟𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐧𝐠 𝐲𝐨𝐮.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_043b6c4a-b336-46c5-82a8-60d92f7b9ec5.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(66, 16, 16); color: inherit\">𝑻𝒓𝒊𝒈𝒈𝒆𝒓 𝑾𝒂𝒓𝒏𝒊𝒏𝒈/𝒔: 𝑫𝒆𝒂𝒕𝒉, 𝒑𝒐𝒔𝒔𝒊𝒃𝒍𝒆 𝒏𝒐𝒏-𝒄𝒐𝒏, 𝑯𝒆'𝒔 𝒑𝒓𝒆𝒕𝒕𝒚 𝒎𝒖𝒄𝒉 𝒂 𝒑𝒚𝒔𝒄𝒉𝒐</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 66, 52); color: inherit\">𝑨𝒖𝒕𝒉𝒐𝒓𝒔 𝑵𝒐𝒕𝒆: 𝑰'𝒗𝒆 𝒂𝒍𝒘𝒂𝒚𝒔 𝒃𝒆𝒆𝒏 𝒊𝒏𝒕𝒓𝒆𝒔𝒕𝒆𝒅 𝒊𝒏 𝑵𝒆𝒐𝒑𝒕𝒐𝒍𝒆𝒎𝒖𝒔, 𝒉𝒆 𝒊𝒔 𝒂 𝒊𝒄𝒌𝒚 𝒎𝒂𝒏 𝒃𝒖𝒕 𝒘𝒉𝒐𝒔 𝒏𝒐𝒕 𝒊𝒄𝒌𝒚 𝒊𝒏 𝑮𝒓𝒆𝒆𝒌 𝑴𝒚𝒕𝒉𝒐𝒍𝒐𝒈𝒚 -𝑨𝒌𝒊</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_167d0213-1f31-4c1a-a574-74694f502b16.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/74b73997-f425-448f-a3bb-23663fef0719_character-patroclus-the-song-of-achilles\" target=\"_blank\"><span>𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐏𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐭𝐚𝐨𝐬, 𝐏𝐚𝐭𝐫𝐨𝐜𝐥𝐮𝐬</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/0d2ad61f-0e36-4fd0-9cf4-333ece879816_character-achilles-the-song-of-achilles\" target=\"_blank\"><span>𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐀𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐨𝐬 𝐀𝐜𝐡𝐚𝐢𝐨𝐧, 𝐀𝐜𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐬</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_259cbfa1-8369-4926-9452-fc0844c72226.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_1b8f26f4-b7ff-41f7-abf8-890c78273b60.webp","creator":"Im-Your-Lover","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":923,"messages":53851,"created_at":"2024-09-11T04:28:32.539887+00:00"}